{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-081","title":"Sentence 81","sectionId":"sentences-081","sectionTitle":"Sentence 81-90","pageStart":526,"pageEnd":532,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":60,"duplicateEntryCount":9,"pages":[{"number":526,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 81"},{"type":"text","text":"In contrast to mammals and birds, amphibians are unable to produce"},{"type":"text","text":"thermal energy through their metabolic activity, which would allow them"},{"type":"text","text":"to regulate their body temperature independent of the surrounding or"},{"type":"text","text":"ambient temperature."},{"type":"text","text":"与哺乳动物和鸟类相反，两栖类动物不能通过它们的代谢活动"},{"type":"text","text":"产生热能，这使得它们可以脱离周围的环境温度来调节体温。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Amphibians are unable to produce thermal energy。定"},{"type":"text","text":"语从句“which would allow ... ambient temperature”修饰前面的句子，定"},{"type":"text","text":"语从句中的independent of the surrounding or ambient temperature是形容"},{"type":"text","text":"词短语，说明谓语动词regulate发生的方式。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"contrast /ˈkɑːntræst/ n. 对照，对比","headword":"contrast"},{"type":"text","text":"/kənˈtræst/ v. （使）对照，对比"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 by contrast 对比之下；（与…）相对照"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 compare v. 比较，对比"},{"type":"entry","text":"amphibian /æmˈfɪbiən/ n. 两栖动物","headword":"amphibian"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 amphi（二）＋bi（生命）＋an→以两种生命形式存在→两栖"},{"type":"text","text":"动物"},{"type":"entry","text":"produce /prəˈduːs/ vt. 生产","headword":"produce"}]},{"number":527,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"/ˈprɑːduːs/ n. 农产品"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 pro（向前）＋duce（带来）→向前产出→生产"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 product n. 产物，产品"},{"type":"text","text":"production n. （大批量的）生产"},{"type":"text","text":"productive a. 多产的"},{"type":"text","text":"productivity n. 生产力"},{"type":"entry","text":"metabolic /ˌmetəˈbɑːlɪk/ a. 新陈代谢的","headword":"metabolic"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 meta（转变）+bol（球，引申为循环）+ic（…的）→改变身"},{"type":"text","text":"体内的机制→新陈代谢的"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 metabolism n. 新陈代谢"},{"type":"entry","text":"allow /əˈlaʊ/ vt. 允许；准许","headword":"allow"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 allow sb. to do sth. 允许某人做某事"},{"type":"text","text":"allow sth. to do sth. 听任"}]},{"number":528,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"ambient /ˈæmbiənt/ a. 周围的，周围环境的","headword":"ambient"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 ambi（周围）+ent→周围的"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 ambience n. 周围环境，气氛"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“爬行/两栖动物”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"alligator /ˈælɪɡeɪtər/ n. 短吻鳄","headword":"alligator"},{"type":"entry","text":"camouflage /ˈkæməflɑːʒ/ n. 伪装","headword":"camouflage"}]},{"number":529,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"chameleon /kəˈmiːliən/ n. 变色龙","headword":"chameleon"},{"type":"entry","text":"cobra /ˈkoʊbrə/ n. 眼镜蛇","headword":"cobra"},{"type":"entry","text":"crawl /krɔːl/ vi. 爬行；缓慢行进","headword":"crawl"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 c+raw（生疏的）+l→对地形生疏，车开慢点→缓慢行进"},{"type":"entry","text":"crocodile /ˈkrɑːkədaɪl/ n. 鳄鱼","headword":"crocodile"},{"type":"entry","text":"frog /frɔːɡ/n. 青蛙","headword":"frog"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 tree frog 树蛙"},{"type":"text","text":"komodo dragon 科莫多巨蜥"},{"type":"entry","text":"lizard /ˈlɪzərd/ n. 蜥蜴","headword":"lizard"},{"type":"entry","text":"python /ˈpaɪθɑːn/ n. 蟒蛇","headword":"python"},{"type":"entry","text":"rattlesnake /ˈrætlsneɪk/ n. 响尾蛇","headword":"rattlesnake"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 rattle n. 咔哒声"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. （使）发出连续短促的声音"},{"type":"entry","text":"regenerate /rɪˈdʒenəreɪt/ v. （使）再生","headword":"regenerate"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 regeneration n. 再生，新生"},{"type":"entry","text":"reptile /ˈreptaɪl/ n. 爬行动物","headword":"reptile"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 rept（爬）＋ile（表物）→爬着走的东西→爬行动物"},{"type":"entry","text":"salamander /ˈsæləmændər/ n. 蝾螈","headword":"salamander"},{"type":"entry","text":"serpent /ˈsɜːrpənt/ n. 毒蛇","headword":"serpent"},{"type":